               <persName id="t18331017-130-person1277">
                  William 
                  Bowden
               <interp inst="t18331017-130-person1277" type="surname" value="Bowden"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331017-130-person1277" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331017-130-person1277" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , gave Ward a good character.</p>
               <p>ROBERT THOMPSON. I had not given Scott permission to take the truck on that Saturday evening; I had not seen him - I went to Ward's house on the Monday evening to ask for my harness, but did not drink with them - I drank with Dentsh, but did not know his name.</p>
               <p>SCOTT - <rs id="t18331017-130-verdict711" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18331017-130-verdict711" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 23.</p>
